Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two were really alone\Nbefore they came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When they were taken into custody\Nnear the border of Czechoslovakia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they were holding hands\Nas they walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They both were shivering in the cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the conditions\Nof the orphanages in the east side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,were horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not like 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh--?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Inge, the bathroom isn't that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's all right...\NThere's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...you can go to the bathroom\Nby yourself, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids really did not know\Na parent's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You only need love in order to\Ndevelop as a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As you say, the orphanages\Nof the east side were quite horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this place was once referred to\Nas Orphanage 47.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But we did what we could so\Nwe wouldn't be controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,by the government,\Neven just a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to avoid\Nbecoming like 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a special orphanage\Nrun by both
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ministry of Health and Welfare\Nand the Ministry of the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The real state of affairs\Nwere being managed by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ministry of the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That place was...Old East Germany's\Nexperimental laboratory...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Experimental laboratory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They were running a project\Nthat would turn the children
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,into perfect soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychological reconstruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Research on modifying humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They made the orphans\Njoin factions and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,observed as they fought each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an experiment to create cold,\Nmerciless humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine what these children\Nwould be like when they grew up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, there's no way to prove\Nthat was happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All the data was burned\Nright before the Wall came down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The people from\Nthe Ministry of the interior
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who were involved with\Nthe Project escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard there is one person\Nwho was able to gloss his record
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and remain in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the person\Nwho was overseeing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the devilish project\Nthat was 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was actually\Na pediatric psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,affiliated with\Nthe Ministry of the interior...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Officially, he was a district official from\Nthe Ministry of Health and Welfare...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,District official from\Nthe Ministry of Health and Welfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Inge, are you done\Nusing the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N-Sweet dreams. Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of that was covered up\Nby that incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That...incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened at 511 Kinderheim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like I've talked\Na little too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me remember\Nsuch awful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please tell me what\Nhappened there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my...\NWhere's my soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.\NIt's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold off on soccer\Nuntil your wounds have healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That man said he was going to come\Nto pick you up soon, so rest until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what really happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The East German government at\Nthe time placed a strict gag order on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It all began with the mysterious death\Nof the director of 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, there was\Na power struggle among
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the instructors over\Nthe director's position...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanage was\Nthrown into anarchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The children's internal strife\Ncouldn't be controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that Johan\Nmade it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And?! What happened to\N511 Kinderheim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone died...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All the members of the orphanage,\Nincluding the instructors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,killed each other off in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a big lie that the world is dark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow will be a good day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hartmann, aren't we going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No...let's take a detour...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't want to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, you're a good boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to hand over Dieter\Nuntil I returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That person\Nwas that child's foster parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also quite the gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Much more of a gentleman\Nthan you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, that boy\Nwanted to go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hartmann's study?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that they were\Ntaken at different times,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but were all taken at the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the man in the photo with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... All the photographs\Nwere taken at 511 Kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten years ago up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the members of the orphanage,\Nincluding the instructors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}killed each other of fin there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, hold on! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that this boy can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hartmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy can't see what Johan saw\Nfrom here back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good... It's no good again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy isn't Johan either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... Everyone died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The instructors and the orphans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All fifty of them died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...watched it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He watched it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...just watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He replied...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just dropped\Na piece of oil-soaked cloth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in into the fire like this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred is created\Nwhen people gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just poured a little oil on it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy, just 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And he pulled it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He had fifty people kill each other\Nwithout moving a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your experiments turned him into\Nthat kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim was indeed\Nan experimental ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a project to raise orphans\Nto become perfect soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking back on it now,\Nit was such a small experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about Johan?\NHim, a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a born leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was someone who was\Nmeant to stand at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could create\Nsuch a work of art!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He was superhuman\Nfrom the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a monstrous being!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He foretold that everyone would\Nend up hating and killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think Johan's goal was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the last person remaining\Nin this world..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...The future is dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to become even just\Na little more like Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you be like Johan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Hartmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot you if you\Nharm him any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know about Johan,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nonce you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's impossible to\Nfind and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you one piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, once you hear it,\Nleave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for General Wolf. He's the one\Nwho first discovered Johan's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the man from the photograph\Nin your study?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the man in the photograph\Nwith Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who brought Johan to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He should know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide for yourself if you're\Ncoming down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot Hartmann if he puts\Nhis finger on the rifle's trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide for yourself!\NMake your own decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd leave me,\Nwould you...Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're my child...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...it's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good... Slowly... Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that you can live\Nwithout me, Dieter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Hartmann! If you move,\NI'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma told me that tomorrow\Nwill be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the bus here and get off\Nat Keunen Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanage is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this to Elna Tyce...\NShe's an instructor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks scary,\Nbut she's a very nice lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We part ways here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A bus will come\Nin two or three minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that you\Ncan't come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...come with me...
